with failure to disclose bonuses paid to merrill lynch executive before the two companies merged under the settlements terms boa was allowed to deny any wrongdoing which they did when pressed by rakoff on the matter of guilt rakoff said the settlement did not comport with the most elementary notions of justice and morality seven months later rakoff approved a  million settlement of the boa case boa did not have to change its declaration of innocence upon schapiros departure from the sec in december  president obama commended schapiros contributions as chair in an official white house statement subsequent careeredit in april  schapiro joined promontory financial group where she is advisory board vice chair in  she joined the board of directors of general electric and in  she joined the board of directors of the london stock exchange group in  she was elected to the board of directors of cvs health personal lifeedit schapiro is married to charles chas cadwell a former official with the us small business administration they have two daughters she serves as treasurer of the humane rescue alliance formerly the washington humane society referencesedit  a b c d sec biographychairman mary l schapiro secgov retrieved  june    a b aruna viswanatha november   schapiro stepping down at sec walter to step in reuters   obama taps veteran regulator to head underfire sec agence france presse december   accessed february    the  most powerful women forbes august     meet washingtons newest watchdog bloomberg businessweek october     nominations hearing record us senate committee on agriculture nutrition  forestry june   httpsarchiveorgstreamnominationsheariunitnominationsheariunitdjvutxt  httpwiltondailyvoicecomnewsmarysusanhallschapiroofwilton  babylon beacon sept   httpwwwbabylonbeaconcomnewscolumnistshtmlprint  wilton daily voice obituary august    lavan rosie december   secs new chairman who is mary schapiro the times london   biography of schapiro archived  at the wayback machi